                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for increasing temperature of furnace top gas of hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace",
                    "一种提高富氢碳循环氧气高炉炉顶煤气温度的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for increasing the temperature of furnace top gas of a hydrogen-carbon-rich circulating oxygen blast furnace, which is characterized in that a combustion heat storage device for combusting decarburized gas is arranged at a furnace throat steel brick of a furnace throat of the hydrogen-carbon-rich circulating oxygen blast furnace, and a combustion cylinder of the combustion heat storage device adopts a high-speed airflow jet heating technology; decarburized coal gas and compressed air flow and are mixed in the combustion cylinder according to a certain proportion, and are ignited and combusted by the electronic spark device on the inner cylinder wall to form a stable heat source. 85-94% of the mixed gas is combusted in the cylinder, and the rest of the mixed gas is completely combusted in the heat storage cylinder. A large amount of excessive hot gas of coal gas and flue gas is sprayed out at a high speed of 110-250m/s, so that strong convective heat transfer is generated in the hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace, and due to strong stirring of a large amount of gas, the low-temperature coal gas at the top 1 of the hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace is uniformly mixed at the top 1 of the hydrogen-rich carbon circulating oxygen blast furnace."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种提高富氢碳循环氧气高炉炉顶煤气温度的方法，在富氢碳循环氧气高炉炉喉的炉喉钢砖处设置安装一种燃烧脱碳煤气的燃烧蓄热装置，燃烧蓄热装置的燃烧筒采用高速气流喷射加热技术，脱碳煤气与压缩空气按一定的比例在燃烧筒内流动混合，经过内筒壁的电子火花装置点火而燃烧，形成一个稳定热源。混合气体在筒内燃烧85～94％，其余在蓄热筒内完全燃烧。大量过剩煤气烟气热气体以110～250m/s的高速喷出，这样在富氢碳循环氧气高炉炉内产生了强烈的对流传热，并由于大量气体的强烈搅拌，使富氢碳循环氧气高炉炉顶1低温煤气掺混温度达到均匀。"
                }
            ]
